<h2>SEVEN 2013: Seven Days of Praying and Fasting for Our City</h2>
<p>United by the name of Jesus, His love for the world, and the passion to see it restored by the gospel, gather with us as we join churches across the Greater Portland area to seek the peace of our city and present our requests to God.<i> </i><i>&nbsp;</i></p>
<p><a href="http://sevenpdx.org" target="_blank"><i>Visit the SEVEN website for more information &gt;&gt;</i></a></p>
<hr />
<h4>PORTLAND CHRISTIAN CENTER:</h4>
<p><i><strong>Night 1</strong> | Sunday, September 29, 2013 | 6:00 PM</i>&#8232;<b></b></p>
<p>For the first night of Seven, we will gather and begin praying at our home church, Portland Christian Center. Address: &nbsp;5700 SW Dosch Rd, Portland, OR [<a href="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Portland+Christian+Center,+Southwest+Dosch+Road,+Portland,+OR&amp;hl=en&amp;ll=45.482476,-122.705398&amp;spn=0.01005,0.022638&amp;sll=44.145447,-120.583402&amp;sspn=5.266307,11.590576&amp;oq=portland+christian&amp;t=m&amp;z=16&amp;iwloc=A" target="_blank">Link to Map</a>]</p>
